Here&#x27;s an example:

{code}
http://bitbucket.org/benhodgson/
{code}

Where you see:

{code}
//benhodgson began following richardhenry//
{code}

Try clicking on "richardhenry". You&#x27;ll notice that the link directs to /benhodgson/richardhenry/, instead of /richardhenry/. This seems to be the case for all "began following" events throughout BitBucket.

Thought you should know!

Richard
